The UK Hub will take place between noon on Monday 6th May and noon on Thursday 9th May 2024 and will take place at the [Sudbury House Hotel][SudburyHouseLink] in Faringdon, Oxfordshire. 

Conference cost wthout hotel accommodation: £147
Conference cost with single occupancy hotel accommodation: £450
Conference cost with twin occupancy hotel accommodation: £300 per person

If you register for conference cost without hotel accommodation there are alternative local accommodation including a [Travelodge][TravelodgeLink], [The Old Crown Coaching Inn][CrownLink] and a few local AirBnBs.

[SudburyHouseLink]: https://www.sudburyhouse.co.uk
[TravelodgeLink]: https://www.travelodge.co.uk/hotels/680/Faringdon-Oxfordshire-hotel
[CrownLink]: https://www.theoldcrowncoachinginn.com/
